### [2] Test d'inscription
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "moi",
  "firstName": "moi",
  "email": "moi@moi.fr",
  "password": "moimoimoi",
  "phone": "0622345678",
  "address": "2 rue de Test",
  "birthDate": "1990-02-01",
